Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我是Michael Henry\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hi, I'm Michael Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾是新聞4臺的王牌主播\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I was lead anchor of the
