Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 你就算站對街拍我\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Honey, you could shoot me from across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什么區別啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It wouldn't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是給我個有防抖功能的手機就有了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Maybe if you had gotten me a phone with an image stabilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那就沒問題了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That would cure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 輪到誰來擺餐桌了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Come on, people. Whose turn is it to set the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我被學校永遠開不完的會議拖住了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Sorry, I was stuck at this never-ending staff meeting at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  意大利面\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Ooh, pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我放了兩份甘藍在里面 你肯定吃不出\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, I put two things of kale in it, but you'd never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸 今天吃什么 - Eve 去把桌子收拾了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Hey, Dad. What do we got? - Eve, set the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 甘藍 兩份甘藍 - 不許站著吃\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Kale. Two things of kale. - No standing and eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種站著吃的習慣一定得改掉\N{\fs38}{\fs38}This standing and eating thing has got to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家正在陷入一個危險的深淵\N{\fs38}{\fs38}This family's going down a dangerous rabbit hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我們不溝通了 下一秒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}First we stop connecting, then next thing you
