Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這招你怎么知道的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}How do you know that move?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遇到你之前我也有過去的 Annie\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I had a past before you, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 爸爸 - 好吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Hey, Dad. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 媽 蒜蓉面包 扔給我 - 不 別用扔的 不許扔\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Mom, garlic bread, hit me. - No, don't hit him. Don't hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 帥 - 好吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Nice! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 掉了我也吃 - 真的嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I'm still eating it. - Really?
