Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 就在那兒 - 蠢蛋們 你們好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I'm looking at it right there. - What up, fools?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放甘藍了 知道你是白人啦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Enough with the kale. We get it: You're white.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能多穿點么 你嚇著孩子了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Will you put those things away? You're scaring the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 Leigh姑姑 - 天啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- 'Sup, Aunt Leigh? - Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頓飯真棒 爸爸 又是一場大勝\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Amazing meal, Dad. Another triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh姑姑 我們走吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Let's go, Aunt Leigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我姑姑 今晚我們是姐妹\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Stop calling me Aunt Leigh. Tonight we're sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們原來的計劃呢 我們一起去吃晚飯\N{\fs38}{\fs38}What about the plan? We were gonna have dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃點冰凍酸奶 或者再玩玩樹葉大戰\N{\fs38}{\fs38}then go get frozen yogurt, and maybe have a leaf fight.
