Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的冰凍酸奶不是真的冰凍的酸奶嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Do you know that frozen yogurt isn't actually frozen yogurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那只是動物明膠粉混上玉米糖漿\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, it's just powdered animal gelatin and corn syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對你家人做什么啊 Mike\N{\fs38}{\fs38}What are you trying to do to your family, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你們要在十點半前回家\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Just be home by 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 就這樣了嗎 - 嗯 再見啦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- That's it? We're done? - Yep. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少還有我倆一起吃飯\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, at least you and me can have a meal together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經吃完了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么形容我爸爸呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}How would I describe Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是賓夕法尼亞人 沒自己想的那么風趣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}He's from Pennsylvania, not as funny as he thinks he is.
