Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也都不整整\N{\fs38}{\fs38}he just keeps it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20年了 他把一切都傾注在工作上\N{\fs38}{\fs38}For 20 years, he's poured everything he had into work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他把一切都傾注在我們身上 好棒哦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Now he pours it all into us. Yay!
