Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為啥要等到22歲才掙我的第一個一百萬\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Why should I have to wait until I'm 22 to make my first million?
