Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是樂高積木 他都沒拼清楚\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Legos everywhere. They're not even put together right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個拖船 什么玩意嘛\N{\fs38}{\fs38}How is this a tug boat? Seriously.
