Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界不需要爛詩了 我就是那個防詩墻\N{\fs38}{\fs38}The world doesn't need more bad poetry, Mike. I am the firewall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以走了啦 我會送孩子去學校的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Why don't you get out of here? I'll take the kids to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 Eve第一節課有生物考試 別遲到了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay, Eve's got a Bio test first period. Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么非要在我學校教書\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Why do you have to teach at my school?
