Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍好了么 多謝支持\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Got it? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們周末想花一天去摘蘋果嘛\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, you guys want to go apple picking this weekend for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我打算花五分鐘去超市買蘋果\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, I want to go to key foods for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5點新聞主播 我們愛你哦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yo, 5:00 news! We love you, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了 瞧我這一手\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Thanks, man. And thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike Henry 全世界最受愛戴的主播\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike Henry, world's most beloved man.
