Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 Eve 衣服不錯嘛 最近在油井干活嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, Eve. That's a nice jacket. What, you working on an oil rig?
