Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快餐食品安全的又一個恐怖揭秘\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Another scare piece on the dangers of fast food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公眾早被警告過了 他們才不在乎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}The public's been warned, Harris. They don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不管孩子嗎 - 這是紐約 還能發生什么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- What about the kids? - It's New York. What could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你哪里得改改嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know what else you've got to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Linda節目最后的那個標語 "尋找快樂"\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Linda's new sign-off. I mean, "Find your happy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前還深入黑幫組織呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We used to infiltrate gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾扶著攝影師的脖子一小時以免他流血死亡\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I held a cameraman's neck for an hour so he wouldn't bleed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得 你靠這個得了你第四個艾美獎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I remember. You won your fourth Emmy for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 Mike Henry\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, Mike Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想你 加油\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Miss you, man! Keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止他在想你 我們都想你 Mike\N{\fs38}{\fs38}He's not the only one who misses you, Mike. We all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該回來工作\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You should come back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 你忘了我為啥離開嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Come on. Are you forgetting why I left?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得那個輪椅事故嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Do you remember the rolling chair thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你老是想著最壞的情況\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If you spend your time worrying about the worst-case scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等它真的發生了 就等于經歷了兩次\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and it actually happens, you've lived it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著這 我與你們道別 和這十一年來\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And with that, I leave you the same way I have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚的告別方式一樣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}every night for the last 11 years:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關注時事 紐約 接下來是晚間新聞\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Stay informed, New York. Nightly news is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你看上去好多了啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, you seem better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我們現在有個叫輪子鎖的東西了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Plus we have these little things called wheel locks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harris 我不想得到一份靠別人同情的工作\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look, Harris, I don't want a pity job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都知道如果我回來\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We both know if I come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NBC會靠展示我的緩慢動作\N{\fs38}{\fs38}NBC's going to milk it by showing me in slow motion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蹩腳的勵志背景音樂來賺錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}with lame uplifting music in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還是新聞主管 這就不可能發生\N{\fs38}{\fs38}As long as I'm the news director, that will not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你的想法挺好的嘛 拜托 考慮一下吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's a good idea, though. Come on. Just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你啊 都沒人看新聞了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We need you, man. No one's watching the news anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們昨晚收視率輸給個叫"顏色飛濺"的節目\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We got beat by a show called "Color splash" Last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那節目就是看著顏料變干啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That's literally watching paint dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike Henry 你是個勇敢的人\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike Henry. You're a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶也有帕金森綜合癥\N{\fs38}{\fs38}My grandma has Parkinson's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我爸爸是個名人 大家都喜歡他\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yes, my Dad is a celebrity, and people love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Blah, blah, blah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家干嘛要停下來告訴他\N{\fs38}{\fs38}But why does everyone have to stop and tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于另一個人也得帕金森的事呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}about another person who also has Parkinson's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酗酒也是一種病啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Alcoholism is a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就沒人去跟David Hasselhoff說\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Do people go up to David Hasselhoff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}因酗酒而得了癲癇的著名演員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們瘋子叔叔的酗酒故事呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and tell him about their crazy uncles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了同學們 安靜\N{\fs38}{\fs38}All right, guys, settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<憤怒的葡萄>看的怎么樣了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Grapes of wrath updates:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}<憤怒的葡萄> 描寫美國三十年代經濟恐慌期間大批農民破產逃荒的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve 怎么樣了 不錯 挺好的 多謝關心\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Eve, how's it going? - Good. Really good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你呢 - 挺好 謝謝\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- How are you? - I'm good. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 請告訴我你已經開始做了 - 當然了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Please tell me you started your project. - Of course I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算拍個家庭錄像 Henry一家\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I am doing a video on another family: The Henrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得如果我能\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I just think that if I could compare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我爸與病魔的斗爭與移民勞工做比較\N{\fs38}{\fs38}my father's struggles to that of the migrant laborers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很能傳播正能量\N{\fs38}{\fs38}that could really go a long way with the healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 聽上去不錯 周四前交 - 在<憤怒的葡萄>這本小說里\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Sounds good. Due Thursday. - In the grapes of wrath,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬德和他爸媽逃離了危險區\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Ma and Pa Joad escape the dust bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸的病就是我們家的危險區\N{\fs38}{\fs38}My Dad's condition is the dust bowl of my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們就是葡萄\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and we are the grapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我們是葡萄還是憤怒呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Wait, are we the grapes, or are we the wrath?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 啊 誰能給... - 安靜點 我正在工作呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Ah, who gives a... - Quiet! I'm trying to work in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才安靜點\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要說帕金森教會我什么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If Parkinson's has taught me anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它讓我知道你不能掌控一切\N{\fs38}{\fs38}it's that you can't control everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后那次新聞嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Last newscast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 現在他們在前面加了個艾力達(偉哥)的廣告\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, they run a Levitra ad in front of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾力達是什么 - 你不知道真好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- What's Levitra? - I so love that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 稍后是夜間新聞 - 完美收官\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Nightly news is next. - And he sticks the landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟Harris說你一定不會回去工作嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}So you told Harris that you are definitely not going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了也只是一個勵志角色\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I mean, I'd just be a feel-good story to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想干份每天上班大家都\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I don't want to be the guy who gets a standing ovation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 起立鼓掌的工作 - 起立鼓掌\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- every day at work. - Standing ovations?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這幫混蛋 - 你懂我的意思\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Ugh, those sons of bitches. - You know what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是 覺得你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I just... I feel like you've
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有點精神緊張\N{\fs38}{\fs38}been a little intense around here lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 采蘋果啦 樹葉大戰啦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}that's all. The apple picking, leaf fights?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡樹葉大戰 我又不是小浣熊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I don't like leaf fights. I'm not a raccoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我離開職場 我覺得唯一的好處就是\N{\fs38}{\fs38}When I left work, I thought the silver lining
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了更多的時間陪你和孩子\N{\fs38}{\fs38}was that I'd get to spend more time with you and the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們都在忙各自的事情\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but now you all have your own things going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好有事讓你做\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I have just the fix for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天十一點到下午六點你得在家\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You have to be here tomorrow between 11:00 and 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要個新的洗碗機 舊的被Graham弄壞了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We need a new dishwasher because Graham broke ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Graham - 你只要幫他們開個門就好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Graham. - All you have to do is let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定他們把主水管管道\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And make sure that they connect the main water line
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連上過濾管道 對了 這樣吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}to the filter line, and... you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我給你留張便條 - 你知道我討厭這活\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Hey, I'll leave you a note. - You know I hate this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我還要繼續忙我的書\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I was going to go work on my book tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 讓我來彌補你一下\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, I can make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次吃藥是什么時候\N{\fs38}{\fs38}When was the last time you took your medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 幾小時以前吧 - 哦 很好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Hours ago. - Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我能省點力了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Then I don't have to do all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 感覺留劉海的都是胖子\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I don't know; it feels like bangs are for heavy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天我留過劉海\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I had bangs last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你就是規則的例外\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, you're the exception that proves the rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過夏天總是你的"大"季節\N{\fs38}{\fs38}although summer is always your biggest season,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 如果坦白說的話 - 真是多謝你了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- if I'm just being real. - Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什么我今天不能寫作嗎 這樣你就可以照看發型\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Is this why I can't go write today? So you can babysit a haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不只是什么發型 Michael\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's not just some haircut, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表明了我的歲數\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's a symbol of my mortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在演唱會上 總有一些傻瓜真的以為\N{\fs38}{\fs38}At the concert, some idiot actually thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老得可以做Eve的媽媽\N{\fs38}{\fs38}that I was old enough to be Eve's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傻瓜長眼睛 耳朵了嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Does this idiot have eyes, ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是他們解讀信息能力不足啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and the ability to process information?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你很難撇開自己順遂的人生\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I know it's hard for you to step outside your charmed life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直視他人生活中的挑戰\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and see other people's challenges,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我這都要奔四了啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but I'm about to turn 30-FF-nna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我體內的卵子(也指"蛋")比班尼根西餐店都少\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I have less eggs inside me than a Bennigan's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒根本不賣早餐\N{\fs38}{\fs38}because they don't serve breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael 你有在聽嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Michael, are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 沒有 說到班尼根那兒就走神了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, no. You lost me at Bennigan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是班尼根出了啥事\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Whatever happened to Bennigan's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike是個慷慨的哥哥 某種意義上來說\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike's a generous big brother... to a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 他給我這樓里租了一間公寓\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Like, he helps me pay rent on an apartment in the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是地下室 窗戶都不透光\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but it's in the basement. These windows don't let any light in,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻有混混能看到我裸體走來走去\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but scumbags can watch me walk around naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為啥不關上百葉窗\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Why don't you close the blinds?
