Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編輯得真不錯 那個漸變\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Great job editing that together. Those wipe transitions:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是看著一個畫面\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I mean, you'd be looking at one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后畫面慢慢剝落\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and then it would just peel away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著轉換到下一個畫面\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and then you'd be looking at something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 太棒了 - 我只是個信息傳播者\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Wow. - I'm just the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不及格 - 什么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I'm failing you. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是你憑空堆砌出來的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}The whole thing was manipulative,
