Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的經歷 而你卻只是拿著手機胡亂拍拍\N{\fs38}{\fs38}what you've been through, but instead you just held up a phone.
