Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為若你足夠聰明\N{\fs38}{\fs38}because if you were really bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就知道此時就該這么做\N{\fs38}{\fs38}you'd know now's the time to apply yourself.
