Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你說的對 這些詩句糟糕透了 - 這是馬婭·安杰盧寫的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- You're right. This poetry's terrible. - That's Maya Angelou.
