Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦補了大詩人的聲音后 這詩真是太美了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, now that I hear it in her voice, it's breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的會議開得怎樣 - 糟糕透了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- How was your meeting? - Awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們甚至已經給我剪輯了個慢鏡頭廣告\N{\fs38}{\fs38}They already cut together a promo showing me in slow-motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以呢 - 如果你出現在慢鏡頭里\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- So? - When they show you in slow-motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不就是你死了 要不被起訴了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}you're either dead or under indictment.
