Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不說話\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're not saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不止是那個廣告嚇到你了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I think it's not just a promo that's scaring you off.
