Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個總能挖新聞的男人 對吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, I'm the guy who always finds the story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須在一個小時內趕到市政廳\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We got to be at city hall in an hour.
