Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒事先叫上采訪車和工作人員啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and I didn't reserve a news van or a crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我得找到個能趕到的編輯\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Now I've got to find an editor who will crash this last-minute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的問題 不是你的問題\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and... not your problem. Not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起Henry先生\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I am so sorry, Mr. Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 你真是我的英雄 不管是工作上\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's just, you're a hero of mine, both professionally and...
