Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有女人能在樹上生孩子 我們也能處理好這事\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If a lady can have a baby in a tree, we can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事Mike跟我們講過無數遍了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike's told us all the same story a thousand times:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在莫桑比克有個孕婦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}There was a pregnant woman in Mozambique...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她產子的那天 她的村子被水淹了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}the day she went into labor, her village flooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在她快被水沖走的時候\N{\fs38}{\fs38}As she was literally being taken away by the currents...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爬上了一棵樹 并生下了孩子\N{\fs38}{\fs38}she climbed up a tree and gave birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和她的孩子一起在樹上待著\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And she stayed in that tree with her newborn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到她們獲救了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}until she was rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不管現在情況多糟\N{\fs38}{\fs38}So however bad you think you've got it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有女人在樹上生孩子呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}A lady had a baby in a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來開門 算了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Let me get the door. Never mind.
