Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在干什么 - Rocky啊 你多大了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- What are you doing? - Rocky. How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}史泰龍主演電影<洛奇>中拳擊手洛奇的經典動作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議員先生\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look, Councilman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給解釋一下怎么20億美元都沒能升級911報警系統\N{\fs38}{\fs38}either you explain to me how $2 billion fails to upgrade 911
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我的下一個電話就打給電子系統部門\N{\fs38}{\fs38}or my next call will be to digital systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小舅子Gerald\N{\fs38}{\fs38}where I believe your brother-in-law, Gerald,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那董事會的吧 話筒是開的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}is on the board. It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,911報警 西4街和13街交叉口發生火災\N{\fs38}{\fs38}911 dispatch. Fire on the corner of west 4th and 13th.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 來吧 - 你就這么讓帽子這么...\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Let's boogie. - You just gonna let it sit like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了 不就一帽子嗎 - 好吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- What? It's a hat. - Okay. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 暈車是么 - 我沒事\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Car sick, huh? - I'm... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 這里非常平穩\N{\fs38}{\fs38}For me, this is perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們剛搞定\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, we just wrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,48分鐘了 他們都沒趕到\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, they didn't get here for 48 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個電話要花這么久才能有反應\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That's how long it took for the call to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還拍到了個救貓咪的消防員\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And we got a fireman saving a kitten,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 接招吧 "顏色飛濺" - 貓咪 太贊了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- so take that, color splash. - A kitty cat? Ah, that's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harris 我告訴你 你是對的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Harris, I got to tell you. You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重出江湖的感覺真棒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It feels great to be back out here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 我從來沒感覺這么好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I mean, I never felt better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你肯定會喜歡這個的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, you're going to love this then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在"今日秀"里介紹你的部分 直播噢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}They want you to introduce your segment on the today show, Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}NBC某檔節目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 首次熒幕回歸 就上全國直播了 - 你講真的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- First time out, and you're goin' national. - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 Matt Lauer欽點的你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yes, matt Lauer requested you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}"今日秀"的骨灰級王牌主播
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可不得了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That guy's aces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓你慢慢適應了 這是大動作了 對吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}So much for easing back in. This is big boy stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Mike\N{\fs38}Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Mike Henry 我的私交\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's Mike Henry. Personal friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了帕金森 真是可惜 可他是個斗士\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Parkinson's. Aw, so sad, but he's a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實習的怎么樣了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}How's that internship doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比于嘔吐我更喜歡哭\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I like crying better than puking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在控制吃藥的時間 保證不會發作\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm trying to time my meds so they kick in just before I go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 能比在樹上生孩子難嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, lady had a baby in a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她做到了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yes, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天有一位特別嘉賓回歸了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And we're back with a very special guest this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是Mike Henry\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike Henry is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和老朋友在一塊真好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's always good to be with old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}新聞主播 Mike Henry\N{\an8\fs38}攜爆炸性新聞回歸熒屏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像你從來沒離開過一樣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It feels like you never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上去在健康狀況的巔峰啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You look like you're in the pinnacle of health.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 巔峰是不敢說啦 - 現在看看外場Al那兒的狀況\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I wouldn't say pinnacle. - Let's go outside to Al right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Al 外面反應怎么樣 大家都喜歡這家伙嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Al, what's the reaction out there? Anybody like this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Matt 我告訴你 貌似整個紐約\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Matt, I got to tell you, seems like the whole city turned out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出來迎接他們的主播了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}to welcome back their anchor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對Mike Henry歸來怎么看\N{\fs38}{\fs38}What do you guys think about Mike Henry coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看外面激動的人群 我好多年沒看到這樣的場景了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look at the excitement out there. I haven't seen this in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從"超級減肥王"來了后就沒見過這樣的了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I haven't seen it since the biggest loser was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}NBC一檔減肥真人秀節目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他回來真好 是吧 - 我才花了6個月\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Good to see him back, huh? - Only took six months to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想出怎么讓他和你在Goldfarb偶遇\N{\fs38}{\fs38}how to get him to run into you at Goldfarb's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和新一代黑人一樣喜歡白鮭魚\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I mean, I like whitefish just as much as the next black man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那里弄的也太糟了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but it got a little farkakt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不懂為啥不直接讓我給他打電話\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I still don't know why you didn't just have me call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike你知道的 他喜歡自己拿主意\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know Mike. It had to be his idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以他不知道這一切 - 不知道\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- So he has no clue? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他也不知道我們的事 - 別拿這開玩笑好么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- He doesn't know about us either. - Hey, don't joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是說你給我開了一扇窗 - 夠了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I mean, you give me a window... - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他的回歸首秀\N{\fs38}{\fs38}In his first segment back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike盯上了市政府高昂的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike took on the city's costly overhaul
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報警系統更新\N{\fs38}{\fs38}of the emergency call system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的Matt 那可是個大新聞\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That's right, Matt. It's a pretty compelling story,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝你讓全國觀眾知道了這事兒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and I appreciate you giving it a nationwide audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要啦 很高興你回來了 Mike\N{\fs38}{\fs38}How could we not? It's a thrill to have you back, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天前 我誤播了一次911\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Two days ago, I accidentally made a 911...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起Mike 我要打斷你了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike, I'm sorry. I have to cut you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須縮短你的部分了 我接到最新消息\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I have to cut this short. I'm getting word right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從華盛頓方面接到爆炸性新聞\N{\fs38}{\fs38}we have breaking news out of Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將衛星聯線\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I want to go live via satellite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白宮的Peter Alexander  Peter接手吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}to Peter Alexander at the White House. Peter, take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 Mike\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I am so sorry, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你做的很好 - 我真的很抱歉\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- You did a great job. - I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本該說說自強不息的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You should've done overcoming personal obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者動物園的熊貓 這種寶可不會被打斷 \N{\fs38}{\fs38}or at least panda at the ZOO. You don't cut away from that gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你還好吧 Mike - 沒事 不可能掌控一切\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- You all right, Mike? - Hey, yeah. You can't control everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你 在我老婆旁邊時控制一下自己\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Except you. Control yourself around my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然揍死你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I will take you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么看Mike Henry的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}What do I really think about Mike Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是得過很多獎的主播 也是很棒的爸爸\N{\fs38}{\fs38}He was an award-winning news anchor and an awesome Dad,
